│ 1. Understanding the Issue:                                                   │
│ The globalopt pass transforms a pattern where a global pointer @g is          │
│ initialized once with the result of malloc and later compared to null. During │
│ OptimizeGlobalAddressOfAllocation it introduces an auxiliary global           │
